sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Usuario
    participant Web as React SPA<br/>(Dashboard)
    participant Filters as DashboardFilters
    participant Charts as DynamicCharts<br/>(Recharts)
    participant API as Express API
    participant Storage as storage.ts<br/>(Drizzle queries)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>(Neon)

    User->>Web: Acessa /dashboard
    Web->>API: GET /api/dashboard/stats<br/>?period=30d
    API->>API: requireAuth (JWT)
    API->>Storage: getDashboardStats(userId, period)
    Storage->>DB: SELECT aggregates FROM tournaments<br/>WHERE user_id = ? AND date >= ?
    DB-->>Storage: Dados agregados
    Storage-->>API: {profit, roi, volume, abi, itm, fts, bigHits}
    API-->>Web: JSON com metricas
    Web->>Charts: Renderiza cards de metricas<br/>e graficos de evolucao

    Charts-->>User: Dashboard com graficos e metricas

    User->>Filters: Aplica filtros<br/>(site, categoria, periodo, buyIn range)

    Filters->>API: GET /api/analytics/dashboard-stats<br/>?period=90d&site=PokerStars&category=PKO
    API->>Storage: getAnalyticsDashboardStats(userId, filters)
    Storage->>DB: SELECT aggregates FROM tournaments<br/>WHERE user_id = ? AND site = ?<br/>AND category = ? AND date >= ?
    DB-->>Storage: Dados filtrados
    Storage-->>API: Metricas filtradas
    API-->>Web: JSON atualizado
    Web->>Charts: Re-renderiza com novos dados
    Charts-->>User: Dashboard atualizado

    Note over User,DB: Usuario navega entre abas de analytics

    User->>Web: Seleciona aba "Por Site"
    Web->>API: GET /api/analytics/by-site<br/>?period=30d
    API->>Storage: getAnalyticsBySite(userId, period, filters)
    Storage->>DB: SELECT site, SUM(profit), COUNT(*),<br/>AVG(buy_in) FROM tournaments<br/>GROUP BY site
    DB-->>Storage: Breakdown por site
    Storage-->>API: [{site, profit, volume, roi, abi}]
    API-->>Web: Array de analytics por site
    Web->>Charts: Renderiza graficos comparativos<br/>(bar chart, pie chart)
    Charts-->>User: Analytics por site exibidos

    User->>Web: Seleciona aba "Por Mes"
    Web->>API: GET /api/analytics/by-month
    API->>Storage: getAnalyticsByMonth(userId, period, filters)
    Storage->>DB: SELECT month, SUM(profit),<br/>COUNT(*) FROM tournaments<br/>GROUP BY month ORDER BY month
    DB-->>Storage: Evolucao mensal
    Storage-->>API: [{month, profit, volume, roi}]
    API-->>Web: Array de analytics por mes
    Web->>Charts: Renderiza line chart de evolucao
    Charts-->>User: Evolucao mensal exibida
